reviewText:
Whoops! Accidentally entered my review into the forum...
Anyways it's worth repeating!  I'm so glad to see that this DVD is available for purchase.  My family and I watched it (from my doula) many times in preparation for my 2nd pregnancy (1st occuring in the USA) and now as a doula myself, I'm adding it to my lending library!!!  Powerful, must see.
